@node "THE_FINAL_FRONTIER" "  "

                    @{b}@{i}Star Trek V:  The Final Frontier@{ub}@{ui}
                                   1989

  Spock's half-older brother, Sybok is on a quest to find God who
 turns out to be a powerfully evil entity.  Sybok hijacks the Enterprise 
 and sets a course for a mystical planet known as Sha Ka Ree which Sybok
 believes God is to exist.


