@node "THE_UNDISCOVERED_COUNTRY" "  "

                  @{b}@{i}Star Trek VI:  The Undiscovered Country @{ub}@{ui}
                                   1991

  The Enterprise leads a battle for peace.  After years at war, the
 Federation and the Klingon Empire prepare for a peace summit.  But the
 prospect of intergalactic glasnost with sworn enemies is an alarming one
 to Captain Kirk.

  When a Klingon ship is attacked and the Enterprise is held accountable,
 the dogs of war are unleashed again, as both worlds brace for
 what may be their final, deadly encounter.


